{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_09_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 夏空に向かって飛ばそう",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "君の言う『夏を楽しむ』って\n……グラビア撮影のこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you say \"enjoying summer‚\"\n…you mean gravure photography?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "本当は全員で一週間くらいオフにして旅行にでも\n行ってほしいけど、多分葵は休まないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really wanted everyone to take about a week off and go on a trip‚\nbut you probably won't take a break‚ will you‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6876569339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "当然だよ。ただでさえ宿題で三週間も潰したんだ\n練習も仕事も、これ以上は絶対に減らせない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. I already wasted three weeks on homework.\nI absolutely can't reduce practice or work any more than this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だから今回の撮影は、ゆったり時間を取ったんだ\n撮影の合間にメンバーと楽しく過ごしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I took plenty of time for this shoot.\nPlease have fun with the members between shoots.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "花火やスイカも買ってきてあるから\nこれで日本の夏を満喫出来るぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've already bought fireworks and watermelons too.\nWith this‚ you can fully enjoy a Japanese summer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことか。ありがとう\n今年は、夏らしいことなんて諦めてたから……嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Thank you.\nThis year‚ I had given up on doing summery things… so I'm happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "手持ち花火に、線香花火、それにネズミ花火……\nあっ、ロケット花火もあるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Handheld fireworks‚ sparklers‚ and mouse fireworks…\nOh‚ there are rocket fireworks too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "どれどれ、この花火は……\nパラシュートが仕込んであるのか、これは楽しそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see‚ this firework is…\nIt has a parachute built in? This looks fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "花火は、日が暮れてからみんなとやってくれれば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fireworks‚ if you could do them with everyone after sunset――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fire-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3199.998474100006,
          "startTime": 62.4999984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "夏空に向かって飛ばそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's launch it into the summer sky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい、今は火なんてつけるなよ？\nまだ莉央さんの撮影中なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey hey‚ don't light anything now‚ okay?\nRio-san is still in the middle of her shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2999984741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fireworks-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6830.000000000013,
          "startTime": 74.1299984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "バカだな、僕だって、本当につけたりは……\nあ、ごめん、ついちゃった。不慮の事故だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't be silly‚ I wouldn't actually light it for real…\nOh‚ sorry‚ it lit. It was an accident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0999984741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fireworks-03.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.333333300001,
          "startTime": 78.7333318074
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "でも飛んでいっちゃったものは仕方ないな\nたーまやー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But once it's flown off‚ it can't be helped.\nTamaya~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "間違って火をつけることなんてあるか！？\n……あっ、花火のパラシュートが、莉央さんの頭に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How do you accidentally light a fire!?\n…Oh‚ the firework's parachute landed on Rio-san's head…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央が怖い顔してこっちに走って来るよ\n{user}君、どうしてくれるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio is running over here with a scary face.\n{user}-kun‚ how are you going to take responsibility for this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "なんで俺が悪いみたいな口ぶりなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you talking like it's my fault?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、莉央の機嫌が直るまで、僕は避難してるから\n後はよろしくね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I'll take shelter until Rio's mood improves.\nPlease take care of the rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4666651408,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2566.6666665999996,
          "startTime": 105.0333318074
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、待ってくれ……俺だって莉央さんに\n怒られたくはないんだけど……行ってしまった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute… I don't want to be\nscolded by Rio-san either… she's gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0333318074,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2666.666666699996,
          "startTime": 108.6999984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、莉央さん。……いえ、違うんです！\nあのパラシュート花火は俺じゃないですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Rio-san. …No‚ you've got it wrong!\nThat parachute firework wasn’t from me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4999984741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5694.126971499998,
          "startTime": 119.1941254456
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "あはははは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影の合間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Between Shoots",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2333262126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうだよ、本当は宿題も課題もやらないで\n学校は辞めようと思ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that’s right. I was really thinking of not doing\nmy homework or assignments and quitting school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（葵、他のメンバーと楽しそうに過ごしてるな）\n（みんな、少しは夏を楽しめて良かった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Aoi seems to be having fun with the other members.）\n（I'm glad everyone could enjoy summer a little…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら、莉央と{user}君から\nお説教だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then Rio and {user}-kun\ngave me a lecture.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9333236695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "大人二人で、子供の僕に詰め寄るなんて\nこころも愛も、酷いと思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Two adults pressing hard on a kid like me—\ndon't you think that’s a bit harsh‚ Kokoro and Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.933321635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（……好き勝手言われてるな）\n（ともあれ短い時間だけど、羽を伸ばしてくれ、葵）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…She's saying whatever she wants about me.）\n（Anyway‚ it's a short time‚ but please relax‚ Aoi.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3765856046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "だいたい{user}君は\n心配症過ぎると僕は思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Generally speaking‚ {user}-kun\nworries too much‚ I think.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.7333145141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……兄貴がもう一人増えた気分だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on… it feels like I've got another big brother now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.5333150226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the Shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.2666442869,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6503924000097,
          "startTime": 165.5332946793
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、{user}君\nどうして突っ立ってるの。君も話の輪に加われば？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}-kun‚\nwhy are you just standing there? Why don't you join our conversation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.033310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ。俺がいたら、自由にしゃべれないだろ\n仕事の愚痴なんかも、言いにくいだろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine. If I'm there‚ you can't talk freely‚ right?\nIt would be hard to complain about work too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.5999771117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "僕は誰の前でも言いたいことははっきり言うよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I clearly say what I want to say in front of anyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.3666280108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、短いけれど、せっかくのんびり出来てるんだし\nメンバーだけで楽しんだ方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's short‚ but since you're finally able to relax‚\nmaybe it's better if only the members have fun…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.633310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "今更、僕達と君にそんな遠慮はいらないよ\n一番大きく切ったスイカをあげるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this point‚ there's no need for you to hold back with us.\nI'll give you the biggest piece of watermelon‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.3999771117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "君も少しは、僕達と一緒に夏を楽しもう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so you should enjoy summer with us too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.2332946775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで言われたら、断れないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you put it that way‚ I can't refuse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3999613442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、君の高校時代の恋バナを聞きたいって\nこころが言ってるんだ、ぜひ頼むよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Kokoro says she wants to hear\nabout your high school love stories‚ so please do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.8666437784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "それは勘弁してくれよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please spare me from that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.7666280108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "なら、今の恋バナで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then current love stories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.2666280108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "もっと勘弁してくれ\n俺にはその手の話は、本当に何もないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Spare me even more.\nI really don't have any stories like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.9999771117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうだと思ったよ\n君も僕のことは言えないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ I thought so.\nYou can't talk about me either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.533310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "仕事以外にも、いろいろ経験しておいた方がいい\n君が誰かを好きなら、僕は応援するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's better to experience various things outside of work too.\nIf you like someone‚ I'll support you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.033310445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "こいつは一本取られたな……はいはい、覚えておくよ\n気持ちだけ受け取っておく。今はこのままでいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You got me there… okay okay‚ I'll keep that in mind.\nI'll just accept the sentiment. For now‚ I'm fine as I am.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.9999771117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "君も仕事漬けの夏か\nでも、そういうのも、君と僕らしいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're having a work-filled summer too.\nBut that's also like you and me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.1291233952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_03-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、みんなが待ってる――行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ everyone's waiting――let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.2666280108,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}